org.apache.flink.streaming.api.functions.windowing

接口 WindowFunction<IN,OUT,KEY,W extends Window>

  • 类型参数:
    IN - The type of the input value.
    OUT - The type of the output value.
    KEY - The type of the key.
    W - The type of Window that this window function can be applied on.
    所有超级接口:
    org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.Function, Serializable
    所有已知实现类:
    FoldApplyWindowFunction, PassThroughWindowFunction, ReduceApplyWindowFunction, ReduceIterableWindowFunction, RichWindowFunction

    @Public
public interface WindowFunction<IN,OUT,KEY,W extends Window>
extends org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.Function, Serializable
    Base interface for functions that are evaluated over keyed (grouped) windows.

    • 方法概要

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void apply(KEY key, W window, Iterable<IN> input, org.apache.flink.util.Collector<OUT> out)
      Evaluates the window and outputs none or several elements.

    • 方法详细资料

      • apply

        void apply(KEY key,
           W window,
           Iterable<IN> input,
           org.apache.flink.util.Collector<OUT> out)
    throws Exception
        Evaluates the window and outputs none or several elements.
        参数:
        key - The key for which this window is evaluated.
        window - The window that is being evaluated.
        input - The elements in the window being evaluated.
        out - A collector for emitting elements.
        抛出:
        Exception - The function may throw exceptions to fail the program and trigger recovery.
